417
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:38,516
I'm just going to say this again,
you know that there's no guarantee.

418
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:40,636
I know, good luck.

419
00:32:41,520 --> 00:32:43,795
Thank you. OK everyone, it's a go.

