Where have you been?

426
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:07,071
<i>I don't know. I woke up on the beach.</i>

427
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:10,516
Claire, it's weird, I feel... I feel...

428
00:34:10,680 --> 00:34:11,999
You feel what?

429
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:16,958
Fantastic. I feel fantastic.

430
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:21,591
- What have you been doing?
- I don't know, I just, I feel...

431
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:24,638
- I don't need my glasses.
- What?

432
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:27,360
I don't need them,
I don't know where they are.

433
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:32,594
I can see perfectly. 20/20 vision,
