434
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:36,309
- Do you... do you have your wallet?
- My wallet?!

435
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:39,358
Have you had a bang on the head?
You're not making any sense.

436
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:41,317
How could that fix my eyesight?

437
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,623
I don't know!

438
00:34:42,743 --> 00:34:47,715
Something bad's happened to you,
and it hasn't fixed your eyesight.

439
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:51,236
Just... just check your wallet.

440
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:54,437
For God's sake,
I'm telling you, I can see.

441
00:34:54,600 --> 00:34:58,639
<i>Tom, where's the hospital?</i>
<i>I'm coming over.</i>

442
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:02,190
Tom? Where's the hospital?

443
00:35:02,360 --> 00:35:03,360
Tom?

444
00:36:15,720 --> 00:36:18,678
Come on, come on.

