00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:30,672
- No, get down.
- Everything OK?

448
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:38,192
- Are you all right in there?
- Yeah, I'm fine.

449
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:45,960
Go!

450
00:37:16,400 --> 00:37:17,400
Jesus!

