460
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:32,880
I mean this place... I know
I shouldn't say it, but quite honestly,

461
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:35,634
I wouldn't lock up
my worst enemy in this place.

462
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,433
I would.

463
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:58,358
Dr Henry Jekyll died
in Edinburgh in 1886.

464
00:39:58,520 --> 00:40:00,829
Six months after his death,
his research notes,

465
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:03,753
plus whatever survived
from his various experiments,

466
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:06,388
